locale.synopsis:
Bishōjo Senshi Sailor Moon Collection is a collection of mini-games presented by the lovely heroines of the Sailor Moon anime.

The mini-games include:

• rock-paper-scissors competitions between the main heroines of the anime;
• clothes-matching: the player must quickly assemble an outfit to match the one displayed on a picture;
• a simple game, in which the player has to press the correct buttons in time to match the movements of a girl on the screen;
• a quiz game; the player has to choose the correct answers to various Sailor Moon-related questions within a time limit;
• a butt-pushing game (for lack of a better term), in which the player, controlling one of the heroines, has to push another one off a narrow stage with the aforementioned body part of the player character.
